ysed the X-ray time resolved\nspectra and when possible the evolution of the optical to X-ray spectral energy\ndistribution. All the events are found to be fully consistent with what\npredicted by our model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2009 20:13:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-05"}
