 cannot be used to derive bounds on strings. However it does suggest\nthat string bispectrum templates should be included in the search of CMB\nnon-Gaussianities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2009 12:41:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2009 12:56:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-06"}
